# Privacy Policy for Calceno

Calceno does not collect, store, or share personal data on external servers.

All calculations and data entered in the app remain on the user's device and are used solely to provide the app’s functionality.

Calceno does not use third-party advertising, tracking, or analytics services.

No personal information is required to use the app.

